713
00:49:37,680 --> 00:49:40,920
la policía, CBI...
lo que pidan...

714
00:49:41,360 --> 00:49:45,080
'No les hablarás
sin consultarme.

715
00:49:45,800 --> 00:49:46,800
'¿Lo entiendes?'

716
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:57,120
